c_branchServices.name: Business Money Market Accounts
c_branchServices.richTextDescription: With Dime's money market account, you receive competitive, variable interest rates, with higher rates for higher balances. As you grow, your account will grow with you.

c_branchServices.name: Money Market Savings Accounts
c_branchServices.richTextDescription: A Money Market account is a great option between a traditional savings account & a certificate of deposit. Talk to a Dime banker to find the right option.

c_branchServices.name: Certificates of Deposit (CDs)
c_branchServices.richTextDescription: Certificates of Deposit (CDs) are a low risk, maximum reward investment at Dime that provide a guaranteed fixed interest rate for a specified term.

description: Dime Community Bank has helped New Yorkers achieve their personal and business banking goals for over 155 years. Every day, we deliver smart solutions to our business and retail customers, by providing financial guidance, personal service and honest value. We offer checking to fit your needs or lifestyle, competitive rates on CDs and money market accounts, and anytime, anywhere access through online and mobile banking. For businesses, we provide loans and lines, as well as SBA lending. Stop by any of our convenient 29 branches in Brooklyn, Queens, the Bronx, Nassau and Suffolk counties.
name: Dime Community Bank
